Subject: [PATCH] Fix greenlet dependency issue and Python version
 compatibility

- Add .python-version file specifying Python 3.11 for better compatibility
- Update requirements.txt with compatible package versions:
  - greenlet: 1.1.1 -> 3.0.3 (fixes build issues with Python 3.13)
  - Flask: 2.0.1 -> 3.0.3 (latest stable)
  - SQLAlchemy: 1.4.23 -> 2.0.31 (latest stable)
  - Add gunicorn 22.0.0 for production deployment
  - Update all other packages to latest compatible versions

This resolves the 'Failed to build installable wheels for greenlet' error.
